Home Screen (Face Mode)
  - "Face Pressure Points" selected
  - Prompt: "What face-related issue are you experiencing?"
  ↓
User Input Screen
  ├── Type your problem
  │     Examples: "Tension headache", "Sinus pressure", "Jaw pain", 
  │             "Eye strain", "Migraine", "Toothache"
  └── Voice Input (microphone icon)
         ↓
AI Processing
  - Analyzes the symptom
  - Selects 1–3 relevant face/head pressure points
  - Creates custom response
         ↓
Result Screen (Face Focus)
  ├── Custom AI Response
  │     • Clear explanation of why these points help
  │     • Recommended pressure points (e.g. GB20, Yintang, LI20, ST2)
  │     • How to locate and press them (time, pressure, motion)
  │     • Breathing tips and safety notes
  │     • Disclaimer: Not medical advice
  │
  ├── Pre-set Face Diagram
  │     • Front-view face/head illustration (primary)
  │     • Side-view if needed (for temple or jaw)
  │     • Highlighted / circled pressure point(s)
  │     • Labels with point names and locations
  │     • Zoomable image
  │     • Optional arrows for finger placement
  │
  └── Action Buttons
        • Start Pressing Timer
        • Save to Favorites
        • Show Another Point
        • New Query
        • Back to Home
         ↓
Loop Back
  - Return to User Input Screen for new face issue
  - Or go back to main Home
